## Architecture Rules
- **Provider Isolation**: Local LLMs (Ollama) are the primary Tier-1 providers. Cloud (Gemini) is Tier-2 escalation only.
- **The Spinal Cord**: All communication between hemispheres MUST happen via file-based JSON objects in the shared Docker volume `/spinalcord`.
- **Schema First**: Use Pydantic models in `shared_schemas/` for all data structures. Never bypass these schemas.